<p>Application Craft is one of the very best ways available to teach students about programming. It is great for letting them build Apps that run on Desktops, Tablets and Smartphones. For student developers, it also runs out-of-the-box with nothing to install whatsoever.</p>

<p>Students can see results really quickly, but it doesn't limit their ability to take on more and more advanced challenges.</p>

