<h2>Your servers ...</h2>
<p>We deliver the system as an Ubuntu Virtual Machine image in Virtual Box or VM-Ware format. We also offer an Ubuntu package.</p>

<h2>... or run in the Cloud on Amazon EC2</h2>
<p>A really good altnernative is to run on Amazon AWS. We supply Amazon AMIs so you can be up, running and teaching in 5 minutes.</p>

<h2>What you need to know ...</h2>
<ul>
  <li>AC Education - Teaching Edition costs just $999 per year including almost daily updates. There are no limits on developer seats. The only limitation is that it can be used for teaching purposes only.</li>
  <li>AC Education - Full Edition costs $1'999 per year and you can use it to build and run administrative Apps as well as for teaching purposes.</li>
  <li>We run a special education referral program allowing you to get up to 100% off subsequent licenses.
  <li>If you stop paying, you can carry on using it but you don't get any updates.</li>
  <li>Look for our dedicated AC Education Forum for specialized support from the commnunity, also closely monitored by us.</li>
  <li>The license is the same as the <a href="/legal/enterprise-license">Enterprise License</a>, but with some extra bits to accommodate the above differences.</li>
</ul>

